metadata.name: NU FANS Collection
metadata.description:
The Nu Series Fans Collection consist of 5,000 unique NFTs that will serve the broader NuFoundry ecosystem by empowering holders with the right to influence and shape the future of Web 3 and its applications via our Nu DAO: Social Impact Fund. The collection gives you exclusive privileges and acts as your gateway to a purpose-driven community grounded by social good.
